{"tid":109198,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"魯芬今晨肺部衰竭離世 終年63歲","createTime":"2017-02-05T19:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T20:10:56.000Z","uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"130230de35566a93adbcd76c4d5cd9ee6d4584cc","tid":109198,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T19:46:57.000Z","msg":"本月2日，63歲魯芬因皮肌炎，免疫系出問題致留院，還需插喉，甚至已認不得人。同日魯芬致電回覆本報報平安稱：「多謝，有心。身體健康！」又稱現時「暫時情況OK，多謝關心。」並謂對於好友關心表示感激，笑稱：「哈哈，好有愛啊，感恩！」<br />\n<br />\n豈料事隔不足一周，突傳魯芬病逝消息，令人惋惜。<br />\n凌晨3時許，魯芬家人發聲明，證實魯芬死訊。全文如下:<br />\n「魯芬BB因皮肌炎導致肺部衰竭，於今日凌晨時分在家人朋友陪同下安詳離世，終年63歲。<br />\n魯芬BB於十個月前患上皮肌炎，從得知自己患病後，她都一直勇敢面對，對戰勝病魔充滿積極樂觀態度。<br />\n感恩各界的愛與關懷，適時公布喪禮安排。<br />\n願魯芬BB早往佛國淨土。喃嘸阿彌陀佛！<br />\n魯芬BB的家人字<br />\n6/2/2017」<br />\n烈火奶奶，一路好走。"},{"pid":"0cb2315a51a83b75b000446dd974e8a9a3465d64","tid":109198,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T19:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7331db4337e1e50b9438ac0705520f8511bcdf03","tid":109198,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T19:48:13.000Z","msg":"Source?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0fd5f11d1e3487658c5d85965b172f2be1f315","tid":109198,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T19:48:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Source?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46248144f191eee160abcbcfe3f19195b25152a5","tid":109198,"uid":82464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T19:49:33.000Z","msg":"見到蘋果報左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif